dc_title_s: [Geological Survey of England and Wales : one inch to the mile map. New Series.] York, solid and drift, sheet 63
dc_description_s: Geological Survey of Great Britain. Great Britain. Geological Survey of England and Wales. Sheet 63 solid and drift. Great Britain. Ordnance Survey of England. North Decimal Degree 54.116700. South Decimal Degree 53.9500. East Decimal Degree -0.7167. West Decimal Degree -1.1500. In upper left margin: Ordnance Survey of England and Wales. In upper right margin: Old Series Sheet 93 N.E. Relief shown by contour interval and spot heights. Transverse Mercator projection. National grid system. "Reprinted with minor alterations 1959.".
